NAME

  **pixelassault** - play a game of Pixel Assault

SYNOPSIS

    pixelassault

DESCRIPTION

    Run this command to play a game of Pixel Assault. The command will clear the screen,
    and the game will run until the user presses q, after which the command exits. Any arguments
    supplied will be ignored.

OPTIONS

    -h, --help:  output usage information and exit

